<bibRefCitation id="EFB84B20AF40FF5BFE48FD8F2AC6155E" author="Makarkin" box="[428,721,602,624]" pageId="2" pageNumber="399" refString="Makarkin, V. N. &amp; Archibald, S. B. (2013) A diverse new assemblage of green lacewings (Insecta: Neuroptera: Chrysopidae) from the Early Eocene Okanagan Highlands, western North America. Journal of Paleontology, 87, 122 - 145. https: // doi. org / 10.1666 / 12 - 052 R. 1" type="journal article" year="2013">Makarkin &amp; Archibald 2013</bibRefCitation>
